				<td colspan="2"><span>Good advice so far, I was wondering if Guard III is a proc or worn effect?
<br />

<br />
I was actually looking in depth at the various melee procs:
<br />

<br />
Force of Ykesha (760 points in guk) caught my eye as it is 125dd plus stun so I was thinking about saving up for that, as I do like the stun component.  It is magic based with a -10 resist adjust.
<br />

<br />
Radiant Permafrost 150dd (760 points in mir) is the highest DD spell and I have enough points to buy it now.  The proc is cold based but it does have a resist adjust of -25.
<br />

<br />
Rujarkian bile 125dd (510 points in ruj) is the cheapest one I am considering, and again I could buy it right away.  The proc is poison based but only has resist adjust of -10.
<br />

<br />
Vampire Kiss would be nice for the disease-based 75point lifetap (1150 points in mm) but I could get 2 upgrades for the price.  The resist adjust on this proc is -25. </span></td>
			</tr><tr>
